<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">In Offense, Giving Thanks</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Sep 30, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Holy God,
</p>

 <p>
Thank you <br></br>
for the one <br></br>
who offends me, <br></br>
for in offense <br></br>
my heart is laid bare <br></br>
and my idols are revealed.
</p>

 <p>
My anger declares <br></br>
the object of my worship.
</p>

 <p>
Is it myself, <br></br>
the empire, <br></br>
or you?
</p>

 <p>
Lord, have mercy.
</p>


